{"tid":1772330,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能泛民提出私人草案廢除功能組別, 然後反對嘅人就交俾美國制裁?","createTime":"2019-12-06T13:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T00:53:53.000Z","uid":137483,"like":126,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0d1c1c343e03a0e70575c8ec986ec9295bb62e","tid":1772330,"uid":137483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無可能泛民提出私人草案廢除功能組別, 然後反對嘅人就交俾美國制裁?<br />\n用呢方法同美國裏應外合，似乎可以促使到<span style=\"color: red;\">立法會普選化</span>。同時，只要廢除咗功能組別，泛民理應可以得到<span style=\"color: red;\">超過2/3議席</span>，可以<span style=\"color: red;\">修改基本法</span>。從而直接落實到<span style=\"color: red;\">真雙普選</span>!"},{"pid":"e2b28669459cf9890a10921fc680c2c24d33f5d9","tid":1772330,"uid":137483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:56:55.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"366d66a36034b8d07b79b7673386989ab4c36556","tid":1772330,"uid":137483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"8ebe3bc31facd8db03fbaaad5c15edab1067baef","tid":1772330,"uid":137483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"五大訴求"},{"pid":"f1730b335061df2019ca16549e04d7c10d4bcb2d","tid":1772330,"uid":137483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:57:47.000Z","msg":"缺一不可"},{"pid":"5444af4cd5134743e73001147d6a141d30b86e75","tid":1772330,"uid":137483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:58:47.000Z","msg":"入嚟幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b85e9d3901713d5998955bbd70f9562e2157ea70","tid":1772330,"uid":73875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T13:59:21.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"494b756a60332b7db6f06efd7fd96cb99267a767","tid":1772330,"uid":36287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T14:00:05.000Z","msg":"有得諗<br />\n推